})=0$) of\nCaffarelli-Kohn-Nirenberg (1982) for \"suitable weak solutions\" of the\nNavier-Stokes system, and we verify Scheffer's assertion that the same hold for\nsolutions of the weaker \"inequality\" as well.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 13 Jan 2020 08:17:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 20 Oct 2020 11:11:03 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 26 Oct 2021 15:46:31 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 9 Sep 2022 11:15:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-12"}
