 PG timing detector with 3D target\ncoverage. Each pixel will provide the PG detection time and its hit position,\nthat can be used to reconstruct the 3D distribution of PG vertices in the\npatient. Our approach does not require collimation and allows to dramatically\nincrease the detection efficiency. Since both signal detection and background\nrejection are based on TOF, the constraints on energy resolution can be relaxed\nto further improve time resolution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 13 Jan 2020 13:17:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 20 Jan 2020 09:42:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-22"}
